interpretation: The "woman feeding baby" card represents nurturing and care. It reminds us to attend to our own needs and those of others with love and compassion. This card can also signify the importance of family and the bonds we share with our loved ones. It is a reminder to prioritize our relationships and to be present in the moments we share with others. Keywords associated with this card include motherhood, nurturing, care, family, love, and compassion. When this card appears in a reading, it may indicate a need to focus on self-care or to offer support to someone close to us. It can also signify the fulfillment that comes from giving and receiving love. Overall, the "woman feeding baby" card reminds us of the power of love and the importance of nurturing relationships in our lives.
